title: ITO offers basic computer course for staff (Los Angeles County Office of Education)
text: ( Source : Los Angeles County Office of Education ) The Instructional Technology Outreach offers an introductory computer course for staff in preparation for the launch of Microsoft Office 365 as LACOE's standard office productivity software.
